      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NUDGE UNIT (1) is in sizzling form lately, rocketing around this track in 22.74 to score two back then following on with a 30.93 win over 530m at Angle Park. In form and looks the one to beat again. SEBON PRINCE (2) tackled far tougher grade latest when finishing 4th over 400m at this track. Was a winner the start prior in easier at Angle Park. Cannot be taken lightly. DAKOTA RYLEN (7) missed the frame last time when fourth (30.92) at Angle Park but prior to that had two placings in a row. Form here sound including three wins. Boasts a strong record from this draw with five wins and three minor placings from 11 starts. Warrants plenty of respect. DAKOTA SHINE (8) has been a model of consistency and deserves plenty of thought.",
